WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.350 --> 02:49.990
[Episode 19]

02:54.160 --> 02:56.530
The Contemplation Stone is indeed powerful.

03:34.990 --> 03:35.960
Qi.

03:35.990 --> 03:39.520
♫That year, that year♫

03:40.230 --> 03:43.440
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

03:44.240 --> 03:47.550
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

03:48.340 --> 03:50.760
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

03:49.690 --> 03:50.740
Qi.

03:51.500 --> 03:54.950
♫That year, that year♫

03:55.320 --> 03:58.650
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

03:56.210 --> 03:57.590
It's really you.

03:59.250 --> 04:02.430
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

04:03.480 --> 04:06.210
♫Layer after layer♫

04:06.970 --> 04:09.820
♫Another year passed♫

04:19.450 --> 04:20.410
Qi!

04:33.290 --> 04:34.240
Huo!

04:48.470 --> 04:49.560
I thought...

04:49.720 --> 04:51.380
I thought I'd never see you again.

04:53.290 --> 04:54.610
I'm so glad you're okay.

05:00.630 --> 05:02.100
What about the curse on you?

05:02.370 --> 05:04.260
Master lifted it for me.

05:08.000 --> 05:09.000
You aren't trapped?

05:09.360 --> 05:11.190
You can't fool me with these tricks.

05:11.440 --> 05:13.460
Chang Mei really underestimated me.

05:16.960 --> 05:18.010
Master.

05:19.330 --> 05:20.690
What's going on?

05:20.930 --> 05:22.760
Why is my spiritual power so weak?

05:22.820 --> 05:24.500
Chang Mei's curse is powerful.

05:24.520 --> 05:26.370
You've temporarily lost all your spiritual power.

05:26.530 --> 05:27.680
Rest here for a while.

05:28.410 --> 05:29.980
Chang Mei sent you to stall me

05:30.200 --> 05:31.820
to deal with Bai Shuo, right?

05:34.480 --> 05:36.120
It's easy for me to kill you,

05:37.800 --> 05:39.480
but Bai Shuo told me

05:40.370 --> 05:41.640
you're innocent.

05:42.030 --> 05:42.820
Chang Wu,

05:43.300 --> 05:44.330
instead of killing us,

05:44.520 --> 05:45.760
wouldn't you rather know

05:45.790 --> 05:47.830
why Qi turned into a man-eating tree?

05:48.270 --> 05:49.940
Don't you want to know what secrets he had

05:49.970 --> 05:51.030
with Chang Mei back then?

05:51.050 --> 05:52.440
How do you know that?

05:52.860 --> 05:54.190
Come with me to the Emotion Tree,

05:54.190 --> 05:55.120
and you'll understand.

06:00.040 --> 06:00.620
Let's go.

06:04.260 --> 06:05.050
Master.

06:06.360 --> 06:08.030
If you go head-to-head with Chang Mei,

06:08.050 --> 06:09.240
-without assistance…
-Don't worry.

06:09.810 --> 06:10.890
I know what to do.

06:11.570 --> 06:12.640
Just take care of yourself.

06:14.600 --> 06:15.600
Mu Jiu…

06:16.530 --> 06:17.600
agreed to be the chief

06:18.030 --> 06:19.520
in order to save you.

06:20.810 --> 06:22.940
He's also the first to find out that something happened to you.

06:24.090 --> 06:26.010
Some people are too important to miss,

06:26.810 --> 06:28.370
like Qi and Wu,

06:29.570 --> 06:30.980
and Ling Long and Rong Xian.

06:33.430 --> 06:34.500
Am I right?

06:37.000 --> 06:38.060
30 minutes.

06:40.020 --> 06:42.750
You're only allowed to hold me for 30 minutes.

06:42.780 --> 06:44.400
Then leave as far as you can.

06:49.350 --> 06:53.230
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

06:56.960 --> 07:00.300
♫You are my distant call♫

07:00.900 --> 07:05.030
♫You are my first and last♫

07:05.880 --> 07:11.790
♫My heart is trembling for you♫

07:12.390 --> 07:15.160
♫In this moment where we embrace each other♫

07:16.040 --> 07:19.450
♫Let's never let go♫

07:25.380 --> 07:26.410
Fan Yue?

07:26.920 --> 07:27.310
Aren't you…

07:27.310 --> 07:29.160
Trapped in your curse formation,

07:29.160 --> 07:29.950
right?

07:30.220 --> 07:31.240
Chang Mei.

07:31.580 --> 07:33.460
You're not the only one with schemes.

07:34.210 --> 07:36.240
I can talk terms with your people.

07:36.270 --> 07:38.040
For example, the truth behind Qi's death.

07:38.060 --> 07:39.770
Elder Chang Wu must want to know about it.

07:40.860 --> 07:41.740
Master Chang.

07:41.760 --> 07:43.630
I've done what you asked.

07:44.270 --> 07:46.140
Can you now tell me

07:46.420 --> 07:48.050
how Qi died

07:48.180 --> 07:49.790
and where the Weak Water Stone is?

07:50.500 --> 07:51.850
Are you

07:52.659 --> 07:54.230
suspecting me?

07:54.450 --> 07:55.870
I'm not suspecting you.

07:56.190 --> 07:58.340
I just want the truth.

07:59.220 --> 08:01.070
That day, Elder Chang Wu said,

08:01.430 --> 08:03.640
since I could make Rong Xian's resentment fade,

08:03.660 --> 08:05.150
I could also help Qi

08:05.170 --> 08:06.870
let go of his obsession.

08:07.320 --> 08:09.320
Rong Xian's resentment was from regret.

08:09.340 --> 08:11.430
He regretted killing his wife and child,

08:11.990 --> 08:13.990
so he couldn't forgive himself even in death.

08:14.930 --> 08:16.620
So what was

08:16.690 --> 08:17.940
Qi's obsession?

08:18.680 --> 08:21.380
If he had died for the Fox Clan willingly,

08:21.900 --> 08:24.090
why would he have lingered here for a thousand years?

08:24.120 --> 08:25.440
Unless…

08:26.000 --> 08:27.660
he was killed by someone.

08:31.580 --> 08:32.820
Like, perhaps, you.

08:33.030 --> 08:34.659
Nonsense!

08:41.799 --> 08:42.720
Master!

08:44.150 --> 08:45.170
Master.

08:45.600 --> 08:46.810
At this point,

08:46.830 --> 08:48.510
there's no need to keep hiding it.

08:48.530 --> 08:50.410
Is what Ms. Bai said true?

08:50.440 --> 08:51.670
How did my brother die?

08:51.670 --> 08:53.300
Qi and I were deeply in love.

08:53.320 --> 08:55.190
How would I have killed him?

08:55.330 --> 08:56.610
You wouldn't,

08:56.970 --> 08:58.570
but love would.

08:58.590 --> 09:00.740
Qi knew very well about your bond

09:00.770 --> 09:02.340
with Ling Long.

09:02.360 --> 09:03.910
When you chose to steal

09:03.910 --> 09:05.380
the Weak Water Stone for Mu Jiu,

09:05.410 --> 09:07.320
you had already made your choice.

09:07.660 --> 09:09.520
It wasn't you who killed Qi,

09:09.850 --> 09:11.330
but his love for you.

09:14.390 --> 09:15.590
Ling Long died,

09:15.790 --> 09:17.370
but the spiritual embryo in her didn't.

09:17.590 --> 09:19.350
It's already strange that this child survived.

09:19.370 --> 09:20.270
How could you steal the Weak Water Stone

09:20.270 --> 09:21.560
to make up for his deficiencies?

09:21.610 --> 09:23.570
The way you love him is wrong.

09:23.880 --> 09:25.090
The one who's wrong is Rong Xian,

09:25.540 --> 09:26.540
not me.

09:28.240 --> 09:30.460
Jiu is Ling Long's only child.

09:31.420 --> 09:34.150
For 200 years, he's remained a baby.

09:35.470 --> 09:37.430
Without the power of the Weak Water Stone,

09:38.120 --> 09:39.480
he will die.

09:40.570 --> 09:42.840
But you can't save him at the cost of everyone else's life.

09:42.990 --> 09:44.620
You're the chief of the Fox Clan.

09:45.270 --> 09:47.270
But I'm Ling Long's sister first.

09:52.980 --> 09:54.670
Ling Long used all her spiritual power

09:54.670 --> 09:56.340
to give birth to Jiu.

09:56.580 --> 09:57.950
I have to protect him.

09:58.810 --> 09:59.840
As for Jingyou Mountain

09:59.840 --> 10:00.510
and the Fox Clan,

10:00.510 --> 10:02.120
I don't care about them now.

10:03.450 --> 10:04.720
If it weren't for Ling Long

10:04.720 --> 10:06.490
to rest in peace,

10:06.640 --> 10:08.150
I wouldn't want to face those people

10:08.150 --> 10:09.720
who spent all their time backstabbing

10:09.720 --> 10:11.360
and cursing her behind her back.

10:13.360 --> 10:14.410
Wu.

10:14.850 --> 10:16.340
Just answer me this:

10:16.380 --> 10:17.830
Will you help me

10:18.210 --> 10:19.500
or the Fox Clan?

10:19.690 --> 10:21.000
Of course I'll help you.

10:21.670 --> 10:22.430
Good.

10:22.960 --> 10:24.460
Then keep the Weak Water Stone's matter

10:24.710 --> 10:26.110
a secret for me.

10:26.130 --> 10:27.440
No one can find out

10:27.460 --> 10:29.660
that I've placed it inside Jiu's body.

10:29.690 --> 10:31.060
How can that be kept a secret?

10:31.930 --> 10:33.300
In a few days,

10:33.380 --> 10:34.940
the Emotion Tree will wither completely.

10:35.130 --> 10:36.060
By then,

10:36.090 --> 10:37.920
the whole clan will know,

10:38.100 --> 10:39.340
and everyone

10:39.360 --> 10:41.300
will hate you for what you've done.

10:41.400 --> 10:43.250
I don't care, and I'm not afraid.

10:44.360 --> 10:46.010
Jiu is my life.

10:46.030 --> 10:48.260
He's the only reason why I'm still alive.

10:49.120 --> 10:50.950
Whoever tries to harm him,

10:50.970 --> 10:52.540
I won't let them off.

10:52.560 --> 10:53.800
The Weak Water Stone is lost.

10:53.820 --> 10:55.030
The Fox Clan won't let him go.

10:55.430 --> 10:57.660
Jiu is so young.

10:57.910 --> 10:59.000
Do you want him to hide his identity

10:59.000 --> 11:00.390
and live in hiding for the rest of his life?

11:03.000 --> 11:03.970
Wu.

11:04.470 --> 11:05.750
Listen to me.

11:05.770 --> 11:07.010
There must be another way

11:07.040 --> 11:08.430
to save Jiu.

11:09.020 --> 11:10.450
Return the Stone.

11:10.870 --> 11:12.950
If you really put the Emotion Tree

11:12.980 --> 11:14.530
and the whole clan in danger,

11:14.560 --> 11:16.210
you'll definitely regret it one day.

11:18.960 --> 11:20.030
I got it.

11:20.670 --> 11:23.080
In the end, you're just unwilling to help me.

11:23.320 --> 11:24.080
It's not like that.

11:24.080 --> 11:25.480
I should have known!

11:25.730 --> 11:27.480
Love is the most unreliable thing

11:27.480 --> 11:28.910
in this world.

11:29.300 --> 11:30.570
Ling Long was foolish.

11:30.720 --> 11:31.800
I was even more foolish.

11:31.830 --> 11:33.730
I shouldn't have trusted you!

11:33.850 --> 11:34.490
Wu.

11:34.510 --> 11:35.720
Be reasonable!

11:35.740 --> 11:36.830
Saving Jiu is a personal matter.

11:36.860 --> 11:37.850
You're now the chief.

11:37.880 --> 11:39.220
You can't only think of yourself!

11:39.400 --> 11:40.550
Ling Long made this mistake.

11:40.550 --> 11:41.850
Why do you have to repeat it?

11:41.880 --> 11:42.670
Fine.

11:43.580 --> 11:44.840
You're upright, kind,

11:44.840 --> 11:46.200
and devoted to Jingyou Mountain.

11:46.750 --> 11:48.440
Ling Long and I are selfish

11:48.440 --> 11:49.950
and unfit to be the chief.

11:50.960 --> 11:52.500
You're no different from those people!

11:52.550 --> 11:53.630
Go away!

11:54.050 --> 11:54.550
Wu.

11:54.550 --> 11:56.410
If you insist on taking Jiu's life,

11:56.440 --> 11:58.130
then kill me along with him!

11:58.150 --> 11:58.950
Wu,

11:58.980 --> 12:00.060
stop this nonsense!

12:03.370 --> 12:04.160
Wu.

12:06.680 --> 12:07.810
Wu.

12:08.840 --> 12:10.240
You know I love you.

12:10.880 --> 12:12.550
How could I kill you?

12:14.830 --> 12:17.050
If you doubt my love for you too,

12:17.950 --> 12:18.910
fine,

12:19.400 --> 12:20.760
I'll prove it to you.

12:34.550 --> 12:36.100
It's my fault that he died.

12:36.290 --> 12:38.640
If I hadn't argued with him that day

12:38.660 --> 12:40.480
or said those things to him,

12:40.500 --> 12:42.100
Qi wouldn't have died.

12:42.370 --> 12:44.550
Love is a knife that kills.

12:44.880 --> 12:47.400
It's the most hurtful thing in the world.

12:48.920 --> 12:51.160
If I hadn't argued with him that day,

12:52.170 --> 12:54.800
he wouldn't have done such a foolish thing.

12:52.390 --> 12:57.350
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

12:59.330 --> 13:00.280
Qi!

13:00.510 --> 13:06.370
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

13:05.090 --> 13:05.900
Qi...

13:06.050 --> 13:07.020
Wu,

13:07.830 --> 13:09.220
my biggest regret

13:08.830 --> 13:16.300
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

13:09.250 --> 13:11.790
is never seeing you wear that wedding dress.

13:12.980 --> 13:14.650
Don't do anything foolish.

13:14.770 --> 13:16.500
Saving Jiu is my own decision.

13:16.530 --> 13:18.180
It's not your burden to bear!

13:17.150 --> 13:22.540
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

13:18.940 --> 13:20.130
Since I was born,

13:20.160 --> 13:21.760
I've been your guard.

13:22.140 --> 13:24.070
My only wish in life has always been

13:24.160 --> 13:25.600
for you to be happy.

13:28.530 --> 13:29.500
I love you

13:29.700 --> 13:31.550
more than my life, more than anything.

13:31.580 --> 13:33.550
I care for you not one bit less than you did for Ling Long.

13:34.590 --> 13:35.640
Since she died,

13:36.670 --> 13:38.180
you haven't smiled once.

13:39.060 --> 13:40.100
My heart

13:40.720 --> 13:42.550
died along with yours long ago.

13:42.820 --> 13:44.750
No, no.

13:44.770 --> 13:45.960
To save Jiu,

13:45.990 --> 13:47.290
you'll endanger the Fox Clan.

13:47.330 --> 13:48.400
But I'll get whatever

13:48.430 --> 13:49.620
you want for you,

13:49.670 --> 13:51.100
no matter the cost.

13:51.120 --> 13:52.060
Qi!

13:52.090 --> 13:52.880
Qi!

13:52.900 --> 13:54.550
Qi!

13:55.890 --> 13:56.850
Qi!

13:57.580 --> 13:58.300
No.

14:04.440 --> 14:06.680
No!

14:05.110 --> 14:09.230
♫The flowers flew away♫

14:12.810 --> 14:16.760
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

14:20.720 --> 14:27.640
♫Light my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world♫

14:28.510 --> 14:34.380
♫On the vast sea, you and I♫

14:39.500 --> 14:41.130
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

14:41.320 --> 14:43.790
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

14:43.880 --> 14:45.610
♫My love brought tears♫

14:45.710 --> 14:47.610
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

14:47.750 --> 14:49.540
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

14:49.840 --> 14:50.970
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

14:51.320 --> 14:53.200
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

14:53.450 --> 14:55.340
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

14:55.750 --> 14:57.430
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

14:57.710 --> 14:59.420
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

14:59.700 --> 15:01.700
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

15:02.030 --> 15:03.610
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

15:03.690 --> 15:05.160
So my brother

15:04.020 --> 15:05.790
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

15:05.370 --> 15:07.470
died for you.

15:05.960 --> 15:08.030
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

15:07.850 --> 15:09.470
Then why did he resent it?

15:08.340 --> 15:09.910
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

15:09.510 --> 15:10.960
Why did he become a Tree Spirit

15:10.120 --> 15:12.500
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

15:10.960 --> 15:13.010
and linger here for so many years?

15:14.610 --> 15:15.860
That shadow

15:16.840 --> 15:18.480
is not Qi's resentment.

15:19.490 --> 15:20.520
It's Wu's.

15:23.110 --> 15:24.570
If I'm not mistaken,

15:25.330 --> 15:26.650
after Qi died,

15:26.680 --> 15:28.530
Wu has been racked with guilt.

15:29.930 --> 15:32.890
All you think about is that you killed Qi.

15:33.260 --> 15:35.360
You think he should hate you

15:35.720 --> 15:38.190
and haunt this place, unwilling to leave.

15:38.680 --> 15:39.960
Because of your guilt,

15:39.960 --> 15:41.030
you come here every day,

15:41.030 --> 15:43.290
telling Qi how much you miss him.

15:44.520 --> 15:47.250
What you can't let go of has become resentment.

15:48.480 --> 15:51.220
That resentment has lingered on the Emotion Tree,

15:51.900 --> 15:54.910
making it a tree that eats people.

15:57.980 --> 15:59.340
I never thought

15:59.940 --> 16:02.590
the resentment on the Tree was from Chang Mei's guilt.

16:02.780 --> 16:04.280
If she hadn't felt guilty,

16:04.740 --> 16:06.380
perhaps this tree wouldn't have eaten people.

16:23.080 --> 16:23.990
Young Lord.

16:35.450 --> 16:36.710
Bad bug!

16:41.050 --> 16:42.360
Come chase me!

16:44.040 --> 16:45.230
Isn't it fun?

16:45.630 --> 16:47.350
This fabric looks so nice for clothes.

16:47.370 --> 16:49.650
I think it'd make a great cloak too.

16:49.680 --> 16:50.750
Yeah, very beautiful.

16:50.790 --> 16:51.840
-Am I fast?
-Yes!

16:51.840 --> 16:52.840
Faster!

16:53.720 --> 16:54.240
Look.

16:54.240 --> 16:55.630
What a beautiful lantern.

16:55.630 --> 16:57.270
Your handwriting is terrible.

16:57.340 --> 16:58.890
Your handwriting is worse!

17:04.579 --> 17:05.380
Young Lord.

17:05.410 --> 17:06.540
Young Lord, what's wrong?

17:06.589 --> 17:08.050
Young Lord, are you okay?

17:08.119 --> 17:08.920
I'm fine.

17:10.589 --> 17:11.660
I think

17:11.910 --> 17:13.599
I just saw something.

17:13.619 --> 17:14.869
What did you see?

17:15.390 --> 17:16.710
It happened too fast.

17:16.730 --> 17:17.970
I couldn't see clearly.

17:18.310 --> 17:20.079
Didn't I tell you to stay at Cold Spring Palace?

17:20.450 --> 17:21.450
Why are you here?

17:21.480 --> 17:23.720
You left me all alone at Cold Spring Palace.

17:23.740 --> 17:25.420
Chen Ye kept bullying me.

17:25.450 --> 17:27.420
I was worried about you, so I sneaked out.

17:27.440 --> 17:28.359
Put the insect away.

17:28.400 --> 17:29.270
Chong Zhao will be in danger.

17:29.270 --> 17:30.200
Let's go find him.

17:30.220 --> 17:31.110
Young Lord,

17:31.130 --> 17:32.740
why do you still care about Chong Zhao?

17:32.770 --> 17:34.090
He only cares for Bai Shuo

17:34.160 --> 17:35.920
and has no idea what deal you made

17:35.920 --> 17:37.790
with Grand Master to help him. You...

17:37.810 --> 17:38.610
Enough!

17:40.360 --> 17:41.510
Since I was young,

17:41.530 --> 17:43.770
I've never lived life the way I wanted.

17:44.540 --> 17:45.890
Now that I've made my choice,

17:46.350 --> 17:47.740
I won't regret it.

17:51.350 --> 17:52.190
Master Chang.

17:52.750 --> 17:53.900
You can't bring back the dead.

17:54.140 --> 17:55.980
Back then, you had no choice.

17:56.500 --> 17:58.240
Qi never blamed Wu.

17:58.920 --> 18:00.210
Qi died

18:00.250 --> 18:02.270
so you could have a better life.

18:03.070 --> 18:05.360
What he wanted was to help you.

18:05.530 --> 18:07.200
If you turn his help

18:07.230 --> 18:09.000
into a cage that traps you,

18:09.270 --> 18:10.900
his sacrifice wouldn't have been worth it.

18:12.330 --> 18:15.110
With just a few words about him

18:15.710 --> 18:17.480
in Rong Xian's illusion,

18:17.480 --> 18:19.440
you think you understand what he truly felt?

18:21.430 --> 18:23.320
Qi's heart was filled with love,

18:24.070 --> 18:25.750
but it was all wrongly placed on me.

18:26.820 --> 18:28.540
He must hate

18:28.950 --> 18:30.290
and resent me.

18:31.120 --> 18:33.730
I have never met the real Qi,

18:33.750 --> 18:35.070
but I know

18:35.160 --> 18:37.070
any couple who truly loves each other

18:37.460 --> 18:39.510
and is willing to protect each other with their lives

18:40.160 --> 18:42.050
won't resent the sacrifices made.

18:43.070 --> 18:44.820
Love should not be torment

18:44.960 --> 18:46.760
but mutual salvation

18:47.160 --> 18:48.330
and fulfillment.

18:49.730 --> 18:50.750
Master.

18:51.120 --> 18:52.680
Ms. Bai is right.

18:52.850 --> 18:54.070
My brother did for you

18:54.090 --> 18:55.920
what you plan to do for Mu Jiu.

18:56.570 --> 18:57.850
Now,

18:57.870 --> 18:59.110
to keep the secret

18:59.140 --> 19:00.690
that the Weak Water Stone is in Young Master,

19:01.210 --> 19:03.690
you're also planning to sacrifice yourself to nourish the Emotion Tree

19:03.720 --> 19:04.890
so he can live better.

19:06.820 --> 19:08.050
It's been 1,000 years.

19:09.920 --> 19:11.250
I'm tired of living.

19:12.760 --> 19:14.390
When Ling Long was alive,

19:14.410 --> 19:16.000
life was carefree.

19:16.660 --> 19:18.120
After she died,

19:18.780 --> 19:20.810
everything in Jingyou Mountain changed.

19:21.060 --> 19:22.320
I still remember,

19:23.010 --> 19:24.620
when I first held Jiu

19:24.650 --> 19:26.520
as a baby,

19:26.540 --> 19:28.220
I just wanted to protect him

19:29.620 --> 19:32.510
and give him everything that should have belonged to Ling Long.

19:33.390 --> 19:34.830
That's why you want Mu Jiu

19:34.830 --> 19:36.820
to become the chief

19:36.840 --> 19:38.120
on Ling Long's death anniversary?

19:38.150 --> 19:38.950
Yes.

19:39.980 --> 19:41.980
The Fox Clan owes Ling Long that,

19:42.600 --> 19:44.230
so it should be returned to Mu Jiu.

19:44.970 --> 19:46.010
But I...

19:47.640 --> 19:49.400
I protected Mu Jiu,

19:50.250 --> 19:51.810
but I failed Qi.

19:52.900 --> 19:54.330
Even if he didn't resent me,

19:55.260 --> 19:57.000
I hate myself.

19:58.740 --> 20:00.410
I shouldn't still be alive.

20:01.120 --> 20:02.950
But what my brother wished for

20:02.970 --> 20:04.820
was for you to live.

20:07.180 --> 20:08.160
Master.

20:08.310 --> 20:09.290
No.

20:09.570 --> 20:10.650
Sister-in-law.

20:13.460 --> 20:14.970
Young Master is too young

20:15.230 --> 20:16.530
to bear such heavy responsibility.

20:16.780 --> 20:18.140
If you die like this,

20:18.170 --> 20:20.140
have you thought about what he'll do after?

20:24.440 --> 20:26.360
This thousand-year tragedy

20:27.230 --> 20:28.610
should have ended long ago.

20:30.130 --> 20:31.680
Ms. Bai once said,

20:32.330 --> 20:33.770
death isn't scary.

20:34.440 --> 20:36.090
What's scary is that the last person

20:36.110 --> 20:38.590
who remembers you also passes away.

20:42.520 --> 20:44.480
I never knew the truth,

20:45.980 --> 20:48.170
and now I don't have the courage

20:48.420 --> 20:49.920
to mourn over another person.

20:51.680 --> 20:52.960
So Master,

20:53.740 --> 20:55.120
please remember us.

20:55.380 --> 20:56.700
Elder Chang Wu, no!

20:58.970 --> 21:00.110
Ba!

21:10.780 --> 21:12.680
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

21:12.910 --> 21:14.980
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

21:15.040 --> 21:16.830
♫My love brought tears♫

21:17.080 --> 21:18.800
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

21:19.130 --> 21:21.050
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

21:21.260 --> 21:22.680
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

21:22.890 --> 21:24.510
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

21:24.880 --> 21:26.860
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

21:27.220 --> 21:28.800
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

21:29.030 --> 21:30.700
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

21:30.970 --> 21:33.080
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

21:33.390 --> 21:34.970
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

21:35.290 --> 21:37.080
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

21:37.350 --> 21:39.360
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

21:39.650 --> 21:41.150
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

21:41.340 --> 21:43.800
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

21:47.530 --> 21:50.090
Ba has suffered for years for his brother.

21:51.090 --> 21:52.640
Now, he's used his death

21:52.670 --> 21:54.600
to hide the secret of Mu Jiu's identity.

21:55.350 --> 21:56.070
Is love

21:57.480 --> 21:59.040
something that brings happiness,

22:00.180 --> 22:02.490
or something that causes endless torment?

22:18.750 --> 22:20.420
The two generations of the Fox Clan

22:20.480 --> 22:22.810
both suffered a lot for love.

22:23.020 --> 22:24.700
What's happened in Jingyou Mountain

22:24.730 --> 22:26.880
feels like a heavy weight on my chest,

22:27.180 --> 22:28.420
making me upset.

22:30.000 --> 22:30.810
Tell me.

22:30.920 --> 22:31.720
If we hadn't

22:31.720 --> 22:33.680
changed the course of things in the realm of resentment,

22:34.000 --> 22:36.270
would these tragedies still have happened?

22:37.650 --> 22:38.560
If we hadn't,

22:38.900 --> 22:40.860
then Mu Jiu wouldn't even exist.

22:41.390 --> 22:42.430
All cultivation

22:42.680 --> 22:44.150
is a fight against fate.

22:44.350 --> 22:45.810
Even if there's only a slim chance,

22:46.370 --> 22:48.010
we have to take it.

22:48.320 --> 22:50.260
The matter with the Emotion Tree is settled,

22:50.830 --> 22:52.200
but the vision from the Contemplation Stone

22:52.200 --> 22:53.480
hasn't come true.

22:54.030 --> 22:56.110
I'm worried that something else will happen tonight.

22:59.380 --> 23:00.730
There's nothing to worry about.

23:01.120 --> 23:02.200
No matter what happens,

23:03.050 --> 23:04.130
I'll be here.

23:05.180 --> 23:06.410
As you said,

23:06.750 --> 23:07.880
any couple who truly loves each other

23:07.920 --> 23:09.750
and is willing to protect each other with their lives

23:10.160 --> 23:12.080
won't resent the sacrifices made.

23:12.300 --> 23:13.820
Love shouldn't be torment

23:14.720 --> 23:16.240
but mutual salvation

23:16.970 --> 23:18.030
and fulfillment.

23:19.050 --> 23:20.240
What

23:20.620 --> 23:21.900
do you mean?

23:22.210 --> 23:23.670
Playing dumb with me?

23:26.610 --> 23:27.770
I can't be too clever

23:28.130 --> 23:29.530
about certain things

23:30.050 --> 23:31.960
in case it's just all in my mind.

23:33.850 --> 23:38.950
♫If the wind intends to fill the sky with flowers♫

23:41.040 --> 23:46.290
♫The moon's brightness is also the result of stars falling into place♫

23:48.230 --> 23:51.280
♫As the wind stirs, the clouds gather♫

23:51.930 --> 23:55.630
♫As the clouds shift, the moon becomes full♫

23:56.240 --> 24:02.560
♫Love is the hardest thing to understand♫

23:59.850 --> 24:00.890
Shuo.

24:00.910 --> 24:01.960
I...

24:02.120 --> 24:03.370
I didn't mean to hurt you.

24:02.960 --> 24:09.800
♫I'm finally back to where it all started♫

24:05.410 --> 24:06.610
Let him go.

24:06.630 --> 24:08.080
I just want to take you with me.

24:08.340 --> 24:10.050
Fan Yue is just using you.

24:10.270 --> 24:12.510
Staying by his side will only put you in danger!

24:10.500 --> 24:17.040
♫All the answers are already explained♫

24:12.540 --> 24:14.970
Aren't you the one

24:14.990 --> 24:16.080
putting me in danger now?

24:18.100 --> 24:20.760
♫I'll owe you all of my life♫

24:18.190 --> 24:20.940
You've already allied yourself with Cold Spring Palace.

24:20.960 --> 24:23.490
You may even be one of them now.

24:21.220 --> 24:24.760
♫But we're destined to part♫

24:23.550 --> 24:25.000
As much as I don't want to believe it,

24:25.000 --> 24:26.400
the truth is right in front of me.

24:25.240 --> 24:31.500
♫How can I downplay this?♫

24:27.010 --> 24:29.290
You're with the people who killed my father.

24:29.320 --> 24:30.730
How can you say

24:30.770 --> 24:32.070
you still care for me?

24:32.260 --> 24:35.320
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

24:32.550 --> 24:33.790
Chong Zhao,

24:33.920 --> 24:35.290
there's so much

24:35.310 --> 24:36.630
I don't want to ask

24:35.900 --> 24:38.810
♫When my star falls only for you♫

24:36.980 --> 24:39.330
because I want to preserve the last bit of our bond.

24:39.520 --> 24:40.000
These past few days,

24:39.600 --> 24:41.190
♫When the heavens fall♫

24:40.000 --> 24:41.790
I've been waiting for an explanation from you,

24:41.540 --> 24:46.630
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

24:41.790 --> 24:43.160
but you haven't said a word.

24:44.160 --> 24:45.640
You lied to me once

24:45.660 --> 24:46.780
and twice.

24:46.880 --> 24:48.150
It wasn't your fault,

24:47.160 --> 24:49.970
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

24:48.870 --> 24:50.800
but if I trust you a third time,

24:50.610 --> 24:54.490
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

24:51.420 --> 24:53.050
that will be my mistake.

24:54.290 --> 24:55.680
Don't come to me again.

24:54.950 --> 25:04.030
♫As you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart♫

24:56.840 --> 24:57.920
Let's go.

24:58.650 --> 24:59.680
Shuo.

24:59.770 --> 25:01.410
Let me explain.

25:15.970 --> 25:17.300
Fan Yue,

25:17.960 --> 25:20.440
one day, I will defeat you.

25:27.820 --> 25:30.520
To deal with both Fan Yue and Chang Mei at the same time,

25:30.550 --> 25:32.950
I have to use the Emotion Tree once again

25:33.150 --> 25:35.910
to provoke a fight between the two sides.

25:36.530 --> 25:38.500
The demonic power Grand Master gave me before

25:38.530 --> 25:40.530
comes in handy now.

25:40.790 --> 25:43.470
It's enough to make the Emotion Tree wither again.

26:09.940 --> 26:11.940
We can't keep this deadlock going.

26:11.960 --> 26:14.330
Jingyou Mountain doesn't want to be enemies with Bright Moon Palace.

26:14.360 --> 26:16.670
Lord Cang Shan, do you really want this?

26:16.690 --> 26:18.190
If I step back,

26:18.220 --> 26:19.550
are you going to get Mu Jiu back

26:19.550 --> 26:20.960
and make him the chief?

26:25.160 --> 26:26.370
Elder!

26:27.050 --> 26:28.650
Fu Ling from Cold Spring Palace.

26:29.050 --> 26:30.660
Elder, it's her.

26:30.820 --> 26:32.330
She's the one who injured our people.

26:32.600 --> 26:34.560
L-Lord Cang Shan.

26:35.220 --> 26:36.820
Let's work together

26:36.850 --> 26:39.070
to kill this…

26:39.540 --> 26:40.470
Elder!

26:40.550 --> 26:42.070
Elder! Elder!

26:42.100 --> 26:43.100
He's dead,

26:43.120 --> 26:45.360
and no one will help Chang Mei hide her secrets.

26:45.870 --> 26:46.830
You're seeking death.

26:52.600 --> 26:53.490
Fu Ling,

26:53.510 --> 26:55.580
what does Cold Spring Palace want?

26:55.740 --> 26:58.330
I can give you a quick death,

26:58.350 --> 27:00.430
but if you fall into Chang Mei's hands,

27:00.450 --> 27:01.870
it won't be that simple.

27:02.100 --> 27:04.640
Why don't you all go take a look at the Emotion Tree?

27:04.780 --> 27:06.540
See what your chief, Chang Mei,

27:06.570 --> 27:08.440
has done in alliance

27:08.460 --> 27:10.310
with Bright Moon Palace.

27:12.800 --> 27:13.950
Nonsense!

27:19.340 --> 27:20.100
Chang Mei.

27:20.130 --> 27:21.920
What is wrong with the Emotion Tree?

27:21.940 --> 27:23.180
Chang Sheng is dead,

27:23.210 --> 27:24.890
and Chang Wu is missing.

27:24.910 --> 27:27.550
What have you and Bright Moon Palace done to the Emotion Tree?

27:29.600 --> 27:31.190
The Emotion Tree's withering

27:31.280 --> 27:32.840
has nothing to do with Bright Moon Palace,

27:33.120 --> 27:34.830
nor with anyone else.

27:34.940 --> 27:37.830
It's all because I failed to protect Jingyou Mountain.

27:38.600 --> 27:39.980
I'm not afraid of death,

27:40.200 --> 27:42.130
but there are a few words I've been holding in

27:42.150 --> 27:43.540
for 1,000 years.

27:44.130 --> 27:45.330
You people

27:45.360 --> 27:46.730
have cultivated for so many years,

27:46.750 --> 27:48.200
but none of you have amounted to anything.

27:49.260 --> 27:51.310
Today, because of a few words from an outsider,

27:51.340 --> 27:52.930
you came to me asking for an explanation,

27:52.950 --> 27:53.710
acting like

27:53.740 --> 27:55.590
you care so much about the Fox Clan.

27:56.040 --> 27:57.240
It has always been me

27:57.270 --> 27:59.160
who has to step in and solve every problem.

27:59.810 --> 28:02.120
It was like this when Ling Long was the Saintess;

28:02.150 --> 28:03.560
it's the same now,

28:03.580 --> 28:05.830
and I'm afraid it'll still be like this in the future!

28:06.450 --> 28:07.770
Ba was right.

28:09.180 --> 28:10.470
It's been 1,000 years.

28:11.410 --> 28:13.360
We've lived for too long.

28:13.790 --> 28:14.920
From start to finish,

28:14.920 --> 28:17.740
I'm the only one who's carried the burden of Ling Long's sins.

28:17.760 --> 28:19.930
You've never truly resented her.

28:20.240 --> 28:22.170
You just want a scapegoat to blame

28:22.200 --> 28:23.680
when things go wrong!

28:25.140 --> 28:26.180
Now…

28:28.090 --> 28:29.520
it's my turn.

28:34.400 --> 28:35.260
Qi,

28:36.730 --> 28:38.010
wait for me

28:38.640 --> 28:39.750
under the Emotion Tree.

28:40.200 --> 28:41.090
What?

28:42.070 --> 28:43.440
The Fox Clan has rebelled

28:43.440 --> 28:45.480
and wants Chang Mei to sacrifice her life for the Emotion Tree?

28:46.160 --> 28:48.090
But didn't Elder Chang Wu just sacrifice himself

28:48.120 --> 28:49.880
to revive the Love Tree?

28:49.900 --> 28:51.250
Why has it withered so quickly again?

28:51.280 --> 28:52.280
Last night, I followed Fu Ling

28:52.310 --> 28:53.320
into the depths of the forest,

28:53.380 --> 28:54.580
but I lost her again.

28:54.610 --> 28:56.850
However, I saw a strong evil aura around the Emotion Tree.

28:57.120 --> 28:58.050
It must have been her doing.

28:59.090 --> 29:00.850
Cold Spring Palace's target is me.

29:01.630 --> 29:02.600
It seems

29:03.010 --> 29:04.560
I've dragged Master Chang down.

29:07.330 --> 29:08.860
All her loved ones are gone.

29:09.040 --> 29:11.040
Chang Mei no longer has any will to live.

29:11.380 --> 29:13.030
Now, she wants to die for the Tree

29:13.060 --> 29:14.650
to keep things from escalating

29:14.920 --> 29:16.610
and to forever bury the secret that the Weak Water Stone

29:16.630 --> 29:17.840
is in Mu Jiu's body.

29:17.870 --> 29:19.110
Don't blame yourself.

29:19.130 --> 29:20.770
This has nothing to do with you.

29:21.670 --> 29:23.910
The Weak Water Stone is in Mu Jiu's body?

29:23.930 --> 29:24.510
Then Bai Shuo's illness…

29:24.510 --> 29:26.440
The most urgent thing now is not my condition.

29:28.090 --> 29:30.680
Since the night we entered Jingyou Mountain,

29:30.700 --> 29:32.420
all the visions from the Contemplation Stone

29:32.450 --> 29:33.980
have been related to the Emotion Tree.

29:34.080 --> 29:35.880
Do you think that means

29:35.910 --> 29:37.020
only if we help the Fox Clan

29:37.040 --> 29:38.440
solve the Emotion Tree's crisis

29:38.460 --> 29:39.720
can we get the next Contemplation?

29:39.750 --> 29:40.900
I can't believe you're still

29:40.920 --> 29:42.360
thinking about Contemplations.

29:42.610 --> 29:43.820
Do you want to die?

29:46.110 --> 29:47.590
I don't want you to die.

29:51.290 --> 29:52.590
I'll find another way to break

29:52.590 --> 29:54.240
the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal.

29:54.640 --> 29:55.810
If there were another way,

29:55.830 --> 29:57.760
you wouldn't have suffered for so many years!

29:58.240 --> 29:59.400
I have my own plans.

29:59.400 --> 30:01.150
How do you know I can't get through this?

30:01.270 --> 30:02.680
Bai Shuo, can you just listen to me once?

30:02.680 --> 30:04.000
Stop being so stubborn!

30:18.140 --> 30:20.140
This wedding dress looks old,

30:20.170 --> 30:22.790
but its color is still as bright as new.

30:23.180 --> 30:25.180
It must be something your aunt cherishes.

30:25.210 --> 30:27.190
You should return it to her.

30:27.470 --> 30:28.970
Auntie placed a curse on you.

30:29.960 --> 30:31.820
I apologize on her behalf.

30:32.110 --> 30:33.400
No need.

30:33.930 --> 30:35.480
Though I've just been here for a short time,

30:35.550 --> 30:37.800
I can see how much she cares for you.

30:39.030 --> 30:40.460
I lost my mother too.

30:41.160 --> 30:42.360
If possible,

30:42.550 --> 30:45.430
I'd want someone to protect me the way she protects you.

30:45.680 --> 30:46.720
I think,

30:47.050 --> 30:48.640
no matter what she did,

30:48.670 --> 30:50.230
it was all for your sake.

30:50.490 --> 30:51.780
Auntie

30:52.500 --> 30:54.010
has indeed been very nice to me.

30:54.260 --> 30:55.510
Her wanting me to take her position

30:55.510 --> 30:56.990
was also to protect me.

30:57.010 --> 30:58.050
Unfortunately,

30:59.220 --> 31:00.780
I have to disappoint her this time.

31:03.250 --> 31:04.330
Well, Huo,

31:04.360 --> 31:06.280
once I help you find the Weak Water Stone,

31:06.300 --> 31:08.130
I'll leave with you,

31:08.160 --> 31:08.960
okay?

31:22.650 --> 31:23.820
Is it true?

31:23.850 --> 31:25.280
Master is going to sacrifice herself?

31:27.160 --> 31:28.560
Of course it's true.

31:28.580 --> 31:30.080
Elder Chang Wu is missing,

31:30.100 --> 31:31.780
and the elders in the clan are all saying

31:31.810 --> 31:34.130
he was eaten by the Emotion Tree.

31:34.270 --> 31:36.980
They also say the one behind it is Master

31:37.010 --> 31:38.470
and want her to pay with her life.

31:38.500 --> 31:39.750
Master…

31:40.010 --> 31:41.560
What should we do?

31:43.890 --> 31:44.700
Auntie.

31:47.470 --> 31:48.940
They're saying you're going to sacrifice yourself.

31:49.140 --> 31:50.190
What does that mean?

31:50.520 --> 31:51.560
You came just in time.

32:01.370 --> 32:02.470
Give me the dress.

32:09.270 --> 32:10.430
There are many things

32:10.980 --> 32:12.700
I haven't told you.

32:14.180 --> 32:16.750
Now, it's time to tell you.

32:19.030 --> 32:19.900
Come.

32:24.010 --> 32:26.220
Master, I don't understand.

32:26.270 --> 32:28.010
The Weak Water Stone is inside Mu Jiu's body.

32:28.040 --> 32:28.810
To save Bai Shuo,

32:28.830 --> 32:30.190
why not just take it out?

32:30.770 --> 32:32.080
If it were that simple,

32:32.290 --> 32:33.610
Chang Mei wouldn't need to sacrifice herself.

32:35.570 --> 32:36.540
Chang Mei told me that

32:36.890 --> 32:38.840
200 years after Mu Jiu was born,

32:38.990 --> 32:40.630
he was still an infant.

32:41.400 --> 32:42.890
Without the spiritual power of the Weak Water Stone,

32:43.550 --> 32:44.690
he would have died long ago.

32:46.570 --> 32:47.680
But Mu Jiu was weak

32:47.920 --> 32:49.960
and needed to slowly absorb the Weak Water Stone's power.

32:50.440 --> 32:51.460
So Chang Mei

32:51.480 --> 32:53.430
sealed him in ice for over 700 years.

32:53.920 --> 32:55.330
20 years ago,

32:55.810 --> 32:56.680
Mu Jiu's spiritual power

32:56.710 --> 32:58.710
finally merged completely with the Weak Water Stone's power,

32:58.730 --> 32:59.830
and he began to grow.

32:59.850 --> 33:01.850
Now, he shares his life with the Weak Water Stone.

33:02.400 --> 33:03.500
If we take it out now,

33:03.870 --> 33:05.340
he will die for sure.

33:05.670 --> 33:06.510
If he dies,

33:06.540 --> 33:07.790
what should Tian Huo do?

33:07.820 --> 33:09.820
But if we don't take it out,

33:09.840 --> 33:10.990
Bai Shuo will die.

33:11.020 --> 33:12.330
What should you do then?

33:17.640 --> 33:18.480
So,

33:19.340 --> 33:20.690
I'm Ling Long's child?

33:21.370 --> 33:22.890
Rong Xian is my father?

33:25.070 --> 33:27.030
I've seen them in the Outlanders' City.

33:27.910 --> 33:30.160
I've seen them in Outlanders' City, Auntie!

33:30.600 --> 33:31.830
All these years,

33:31.980 --> 33:34.190
I should have told you everything,

33:34.610 --> 33:35.970
but I couldn't let anyone know

33:35.990 --> 33:37.690
the secret of the Weak Water Stone.

33:37.740 --> 33:38.920
When I found out that Fan Yue

33:38.920 --> 33:40.720
came for the Weak Water Stone,

33:40.720 --> 33:42.880
I feared Tian Huo would harm you.

33:43.280 --> 33:44.250
Jiu,

33:44.580 --> 33:45.900
everything I did

33:46.360 --> 33:47.960
was just to protect you.

33:48.450 --> 33:50.290
The Emotion Tree can't wither,

33:50.920 --> 33:52.400
and I can't die.

33:53.490 --> 33:54.920
So you've kept everything a secret

33:54.940 --> 33:56.260
for so many years.

33:56.290 --> 33:58.180
Now, to keep my secret buried,

33:58.820 --> 34:01.220
you're going to sacrifice yourself!

34:02.660 --> 34:03.860
Silly boy.

34:04.570 --> 34:06.230
I'm just tired.

34:08.630 --> 34:09.940
To live

34:10.409 --> 34:12.650
means to have something to look forward to.

34:14.620 --> 34:17.330
When Ling Long first passed away,

34:17.360 --> 34:19.820
there was a question I thought about for a long time.

34:19.900 --> 34:21.159
At that time, Rong Xian

34:21.389 --> 34:23.850
pierced her body with his sword.

34:24.880 --> 34:26.199
If she had the strength

34:26.219 --> 34:27.820
to make you survive,

34:29.050 --> 34:30.940
why didn't she save herself?

34:30.580 --> 34:33.969
♫Don't linger, don't regret♫

34:31.940 --> 34:33.790
She used her strength

34:34.370 --> 34:35.570
to save me.

34:34.929 --> 34:37.460
♫The last moonlight♫

34:35.670 --> 34:36.860
Not only that.

34:37.350 --> 34:39.620
I later learned that,

34:38.389 --> 34:42.010
♫The water from my hometown flows gently♫

34:39.650 --> 34:40.940
at that time,

34:40.960 --> 34:42.250
her heart had already died.

34:43.179 --> 34:45.969
♫Sending me to the distant place♫

34:43.850 --> 34:45.300
If the heart is dead,

34:46.350 --> 34:48.290
what's the point of keeping the body alive?

34:46.500 --> 34:50.610
♫In this life, at this time♫

34:49.949 --> 34:51.469
After Qi died,

34:50.850 --> 34:54.320
♫I dare not look back♫

34:51.949 --> 34:53.469
my heart also died.

34:55.100 --> 34:58.320
♫Is there the same moonlight♫

34:56.280 --> 34:57.950
But I couldn't die.

34:58.590 --> 35:00.590
If I died, what would happen to you?

34:59.330 --> 35:02.550
♫On your path?♫

35:01.080 --> 35:03.660
So I wanted you to grow up quickly

35:03.380 --> 35:06.420
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

35:03.830 --> 35:05.490
and learn magic

35:05.510 --> 35:06.460
so you could protect yourself.

35:06.480 --> 35:08.690
I wanted you to be sensible and strong

35:06.950 --> 35:10.200
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

35:08.720 --> 35:10.320
so that one day, when I was gone,

35:10.880 --> 35:12.760
you'd be able to protect yourself.

35:11.070 --> 35:12.930
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

35:12.780 --> 35:13.540
Auntie.

35:13.580 --> 35:15.140
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

35:14.140 --> 35:15.320
I was wrong.

35:15.400 --> 35:18.190
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

35:15.800 --> 35:18.280
I should've listened to you and trained harder.

35:18.300 --> 35:19.740
If I had, maybe things wouldn't…

35:19.080 --> 35:22.110
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

35:20.260 --> 35:21.010
No.

35:21.420 --> 35:22.630
I was wrong.

35:22.300 --> 35:25.690
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

35:23.560 --> 35:25.760
I only wanted to make you strong

35:25.780 --> 35:27.830
but forgot to make you happy.

35:26.410 --> 35:28.540
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

35:28.250 --> 35:29.660
If it weren't for Ms. Bai who reminded me,

35:28.900 --> 35:30.730
♫Time after time♫

35:29.710 --> 35:30.960
I'd have forgotten it.

35:31.540 --> 35:36.360
♫Oh, melancholy♫

35:31.890 --> 35:34.010
Before Ling Long died,

35:34.030 --> 35:36.280
she didn't want me to return to Jingyou Mountain.

35:37.220 --> 35:39.400
She wanted me to live the life I wanted.

35:40.820 --> 35:42.660
But I didn't treat you the same way.

35:42.690 --> 35:44.330
It doesn't matter, Auntie.

35:44.730 --> 35:45.650
It doesn't matter anymore.

35:46.580 --> 35:47.950
When I was young

35:47.620 --> 35:51.010
♫Don't linger, don't regret♫

35:48.300 --> 35:49.920
and others mocked me

35:50.540 --> 35:52.880
because I had no parents,

35:52.040 --> 35:54.400
♫The last moonlight♫

35:52.910 --> 35:54.900
I'd always follow you around and ask you

35:55.170 --> 35:58.840
♫The water from my hometown flows gently♫

35:55.380 --> 35:56.750
who my parents were.

35:58.030 --> 35:59.520
Back then, you told me

35:59.930 --> 36:01.490
it doesn't matter who my parents are;

36:00.050 --> 36:02.580
♫Sending me to the distant place♫

36:02.640 --> 36:04.270
what matters is who I am.

36:03.270 --> 36:07.190
♫In this life, at this time♫

36:04.990 --> 36:06.990
I've kept those words in my heart.

36:07.490 --> 36:09.010
In the past, I was always told what to do,

36:07.750 --> 36:10.960
♫I dare not look back♫

36:09.580 --> 36:11.140
so I wanted freedom.

36:11.970 --> 36:12.920
I had no parents,

36:12.140 --> 36:15.360
♫Is there the same moonlight♫

36:12.920 --> 36:14.070
so I wanted a family.

36:14.650 --> 36:15.650
But now,

36:16.300 --> 36:19.300
♫On your path?♫

36:16.800 --> 36:18.040
I have everything.

36:20.100 --> 36:23.140
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

36:20.660 --> 36:22.740
I'm living the life I've always wanted.

36:23.690 --> 36:26.970
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

36:28.020 --> 36:29.280
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

36:30.120 --> 36:31.470
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

36:31.810 --> 36:35.130
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

36:35.060 --> 36:37.540
Ling Long gave me life,

36:35.810 --> 36:39.340
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

36:38.670 --> 36:41.280
and Fan Yue saved me,

36:39.760 --> 36:43.030
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

36:41.560 --> 36:44.550
but it was you, Auntie, who raised me.

36:43.890 --> 36:45.720
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

36:46.070 --> 36:49.900
♫Time after time♫

36:52.760 --> 36:56.510
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

36:53.740 --> 36:55.300
I'm sorry for being a bad son,

36:56.760 --> 37:00.220
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

36:57.570 --> 36:59.020
Mother.

37:00.450 --> 37:02.530
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

37:02.960 --> 37:04.530
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

37:04.860 --> 37:08.610
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

37:09.030 --> 37:12.790
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

37:13.110 --> 37:16.150
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

37:16.670 --> 37:18.810
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

37:43.550 --> 37:44.510
Young Lord,

37:44.640 --> 37:46.030
we can kill humans to refine

37:46.050 --> 37:47.280
the evil insect for you.

37:47.420 --> 37:49.200
You don't have to come in person.

37:50.030 --> 37:51.760
The evil insect will be fully grown soon.

37:51.780 --> 37:53.570
I must witness

37:53.600 --> 37:55.480
the moment of its completion.

37:55.500 --> 37:57.420
There are so many human cities.

37:57.450 --> 37:59.220
Why have you chosen Ning'an City specifically?

38:01.270 --> 38:03.830
Don't you find this city interesting?

38:03.860 --> 38:05.330
It's a small city,

38:05.360 --> 38:06.650
but a divine stone appeared here;

38:06.670 --> 38:08.150
its people survived the Nether Poison;

38:08.180 --> 38:10.420
a local girl absorbed the divine stone;

38:11.280 --> 38:13.540
and a Demon King opened a restaurant here.

38:13.560 --> 38:16.350
I've heard a lot about the luxurious Unbridled Pavilion.

38:16.290 --> 38:18.270
[Unbridled Pavilion]

38:16.600 --> 38:18.170
Since I'm out,

38:18.190 --> 38:19.540
I have to check it out myself.

38:20.490 --> 38:21.850
After all,

38:21.880 --> 38:24.970
the new battle is about to begin.

38:26.310 --> 38:27.800
Governor.

38:28.380 --> 38:29.460
Greetings, Governor.

38:30.750 --> 38:32.020
How's business been recently?

38:32.050 --> 38:32.930
Business is good.

38:32.950 --> 38:34.350
Bai Xun died

38:34.380 --> 38:35.710
in the Nether Poison chaos,

38:35.900 --> 38:37.420
and there's a new governor so soon.

38:37.450 --> 38:38.050
Take a look.

38:38.070 --> 38:39.400
In a few years,

38:39.420 --> 38:41.670
who will even remember Bai Xun's name?

38:41.700 --> 38:44.180
No one will care for anyone forever.

38:44.760 --> 38:46.870
If you give your life for someone unworthy,

38:47.080 --> 38:48.340
it'll just end up

38:48.700 --> 38:50.340
as a joke.

38:52.110 --> 38:53.870
If we take this new governor's life

38:53.890 --> 38:55.850
to complete the evil insect's refinement,

38:55.940 --> 38:57.970
at least his death will have meaning.

39:20.070 --> 39:21.640
Governor, there's a bug.

39:21.660 --> 39:22.670
It's poisonous.

39:22.910 --> 39:24.120
An Eternal!

39:24.600 --> 39:25.250
Let's go.

39:25.700 --> 39:26.600
Sir,

39:26.780 --> 39:28.410
you look kind.

39:28.440 --> 39:30.200
Is this your first time visiting Ning'an City?

39:59.210 --> 40:00.590
It's really you,

40:00.610 --> 40:02.300
a demon from Cold Spring Palace.

40:02.330 --> 40:05.000
Instead of staying in your sect,

40:05.020 --> 40:06.780
why have you come to this small city?

40:06.820 --> 40:07.890
If I hadn't come,

40:07.920 --> 40:09.830
you'd be harming the humans here.

40:10.170 --> 40:11.170
Tell me!

40:11.200 --> 40:12.980
Were you the one behind the murders

40:13.030 --> 40:14.170
in the three cities to the west?

40:14.230 --> 40:16.250
Only someone like me

40:16.280 --> 40:17.480
could pull off

40:17.510 --> 40:18.650
such a masterpiece.

40:18.670 --> 40:19.840
How arrogant!

40:20.130 --> 40:22.390
I'll kill you right here today

40:22.670 --> 40:24.190
to eliminate any future threat!

40:51.230 --> 40:52.200
This cup of tea

40:52.280 --> 40:53.800
is for my years of unfilial behavior.

40:53.870 --> 40:55.200
You've loved me unconditionally

40:55.840 --> 40:57.280
and never reproached me.

41:11.740 --> 41:12.720
This cup

41:12.750 --> 41:14.460
is for my foolishness in youth,

41:15.130 --> 41:16.610
which led to so many troubles.

41:16.640 --> 41:18.420
You've shielded me from all storms.

41:28.680 --> 41:30.020
The last cup

41:30.050 --> 41:32.130
is for you sacrificing everything

41:33.790 --> 41:35.630
so I could live these 20 years without worry.

41:35.660 --> 41:37.830
There shouldn't have been Mu Jiu in this world.

41:39.160 --> 41:40.470
There should have been only Wu.

41:41.510 --> 41:42.680
Mu Jiu was born,

41:43.520 --> 41:44.880
but Wu died.

41:46.050 --> 41:48.700
It shouldn't have been me who was innocent and carefree.

41:49.210 --> 41:50.760
It shouldn't have been me who could travel around

41:50.760 --> 41:51.760
with the person I love.

41:53.640 --> 41:54.790
I'm sorry.

42:01.530 --> 42:02.710
Silly boy.

42:03.130 --> 42:04.210
Go now.

42:05.180 --> 42:06.960
I should have let you go long ago.

42:07.210 --> 42:09.170
And then leave you here to die alone?

42:09.760 --> 42:11.540
Should I live the rest of my life in guilt,

42:11.560 --> 42:14.030
just like you did?

42:14.580 --> 42:16.020
I don't want that.

42:16.890 --> 42:18.890
I've already lost my mother.

42:18.910 --> 42:20.040
This time,

42:20.920 --> 42:22.590
I won't let you die.

42:29.600 --> 42:30.770
Jiu,

42:31.210 --> 42:32.320
the tea…

42:32.890 --> 42:34.180
I'm sorry, Auntie.

42:34.610 --> 42:36.840
I placed a curse in the tea.

42:37.630 --> 42:39.500
I shouldn't have taken advantage of your trust,

42:39.530 --> 42:41.310
but I also want to protect you,

42:41.800 --> 42:43.190
even if only this once.

42:44.010 --> 42:45.140
No.

42:45.790 --> 42:47.150
Jiu, no.

43:03.520 --> 43:05.210
This time,

43:06.170 --> 43:07.700
let me protect you.
